Depends: solo5 (>= 0.8) | solo5-hvt, iproute2
Recommends: jq, docker.io | containerd
Description: OCI runtime for Solo5 unikernels
 aussi is an OCI-compatible container runtime that launches Solo5
 unikernels using solo5-hvt instead of standard Linux containers.
 .
 It integrates with Docker and containerd, automatically manages TAP
 network interfaces, and validates unikernel manifests before launch.
